d":"4d2932063acc2cf37f2c771227ed4bdfec72e21f","tid":1776293,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"062bab388e0e8d431ff564a47c9518968056e76f","tid":1776293,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"比起其他區啲泛民議員，呢個巴打又真係弱咗啲，但既然佢有心選又選到，就一齊努力幫下佢。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"但下屆真心唔好選..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"你都on9<br />\n佢地任期4年, 依家都未上任你就睇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb0b61b04afb97cd01b7b7b123d7e207661ea60","tid":1776293,"uid":127553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=6d58dc06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg:shorturl.at/fgluV"},{"pid":"3637af992494fcc1026a562d7345b2cb7d7943eb","tid":1776293,"uid":199261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b04f539c539c5394db0558ac6a2d8920c5e4ee09","tid":1776293,"uid":308486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aaf9b5ec7fffb9b3a2a7e58cf2749f0dd224f404","tid":1776293,"uid":221265,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"3e365607d0ff68899497d454d78e86c7bcc4baff","tid":1776293,"uid":308486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"成段訪問內容一開始首先介紹佢係政治素人，強調佢會考零分，做7仔兼職，話佢自稱社區幹事，但做過啲乜嘢又唔願意透露，剩係話做過泛民嘅義工。<br />\n比我感覺係TVB有意講到佢咁廢、零經驗都做到區議員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:係兩老開住TVB黎睇，我先聽到啲內容<br />\n結果啲廢老睇完就猛咁話弱智都選到做議員，識撚做嘢咩，啲選民為投而投唔用腦。做完今屆下屆咪又選唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:11:12.000Z","msg":"Tvb你想點？<br />\n唔直接話佢弱智咪算不偏不倚<br />\n做咩仲睇？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"屋企個廢老要睇，我一轉台佢就勁燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"佢唔係你屋企人。"},{"pid":"7193dcdb717eba66ee0b8bcfaa3b9e12075ea467","tid":1776293,"uid":58998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"唔係睇唔睇死，係對家等緊佢出醜，仲會係無限放大咗嗰隻<br />\n咁嘅學歷一定成為對家攻擊對象，正如如果對家有個咁嘅議員，我地一定會笑佢一樣<br />\n而且油麻地品流咁雜，對家一地瘋狂玩嘢<br />\n以佢能力真係好難搞<br />\n惟有希望泛民有經驗可以幫下佢"},{"pid":"22c81f82508023576b7116baf01c822e7f4b0853","tid":1776293,"uid":20870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1ba354ba1ac83b384d72c7d9527b7bdf87050269","tid":1776293,"uid":2889,"like":3,"dislike":53,"score":-50,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"認真一問 有冇連登仔見到佢都當選到 3萬蚊一個月 個刻真係有後悔無試下去選區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就真係有一刻係唸過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地又未開始做 單憑人地訪問就下定論？<br />\n記住點都好做好地區工作 我地有眼睇"},{"pid":"eddd9c4db95012469cacce6cc8fa515d2ba602b9","tid":1776293,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7193dcdb717eba66ee0b8bcfaa3b9e12075ea467","tid":1776293,"uid":58998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"唔係睇唔睇死，係對家等緊佢出醜，仲會係無限放大咗嗰隻<br />\n咁嘅學歷一定